a(S"Van Gogh occasionally visited Caf  du Tambourin run by Agostina Segatori, the subject of this painting. Previously an artist's model[10] to Manet and Corot and others,[11] the Naples-born Agostina saved the money she earned working as a model and opened the Italian themed Caf  du Tambourin in 1885, which particularly catered to artists.[12]"
p1037
