a(S"Portrait of Dr. Gachet is one of the most revered paintings by Dutch artist Vincent van Gogh of Dr. Paul Gachet, who took care of him in his last months. In 1990, it fetched a record price of  82.5 million ( 75 million, plus a 10 percent buyer's commission).[45]"
p1583
