a(S'Both Farmhouse in a Wheat Field[35] and Farmhouses in Wheat Field Near Arles were made in May, 1888[36] which Van Gogh described at the time: "A little town surrounded by fields completely blooming with yellow and purple flowers; you know, it is a beautiful Japanese dream."[37]'
