a(S'When I hear you talk about a lot of new names, it s not always possible for me to understand when I ve seen absolutely nothing by them. And from what you said about Impressionism , I ve grasped that it s something different from what I thought it was, but it s still not entirely clear to me what one should understand by it.'
p4258
