a(S'Before Vincent painted The Potato Eaters Isra ls had already treated the same subject in his A Peasant Family at the Table[11] and judging from comment in a letter to Theo 11 March 1882 Vincent had seen this (or at least a variation of it) [12] and had been inspired by it to produce his own version of it. Compositionally the two are very similar:in both paintings the composition of the painting is centered by a figure whose back is turned to us.'
