tp6098
a(g34
g2
tp6099
a(S'Methods of preservation exist, including the translation of a work from an obsolete medium into a related new medium,[13] the digital archiving of media (see Internet Archive), and the use of emulators to preserve work dependent on obsolete software or operating system environments.[14]'
