a(S'In New Media programs, students are able to get acquainted with the newest forms of creation and communication. New Media students learn to identify what is or isn\'t "new" about certain technologies.[15] Science and the market will always present new tools and platforms for artists and designers. Students learn how to sort through new emerging technological platforms and place them in a larger context of sensation, communication, production, and consumption.'
p6105
