a(S'Pitch standards and Standard pitch[edit]'
p9461
g2
tp9462
a(S'Main article: Concert pitch'
p9463
g2
tp9464
a(S'A pitch standard (also Concert pitch) is the conventional pitch reference a group of musical instruments are tuned to for a performance. Concert pitch may vary from ensemble to ensemble, and has varied widely over musical history.'
p9465
g2
tp9466
