a(S'In his Newsweek article "The Problem With Jazz Criticism",[170] Stanley Crouch considers Miles Davis\' playing of fusion to be a turning point that led to smooth jazz. Critic Aaron J. West has countered the often negative perceptions of smooth jazz, stating:'
