g2
tp17630
a(S'have the responsibility to store objects, museums develop taxonomies for '
p17631
g2
tp17632
a(S'their collections, using conventions of classification authority for the sake of '
p17633
g2
tp17634
a(S'consistency. This may be undertaken with the museum  s archivist. The '
p17635
g2
