g2
tp17685
a(S'In addition to upstanding practices, a black market exists for great art, which '
p17686
g2
tp17687
a(S'is closely tied to art theft and art forgery. No auction houses or dealers admit '
p17688
g2
tp17689
a(S'openly to participating in the black market because of its illegality, but expos '
