p17713
g2
tp17714
a(S'national superiority or love of one  s country. Russian art is an especially '
p17715
g2
tp17716
a(S'good example of this, as the Russian avant  garde and later Soviet art were '
p17717
g2
tp17718
a(S'attempts to define that country  s identity.'
