p17724
g2
tp17725
a(S'For example, someone might specialize in the 19th  century German or '
p17726
g2
tp17727
a(S'contemporary Chinese art history. A focus on nationhood has deep roots in '
p17728
g2
tp17729
a(S"the discipline. Indeed, Vasari's Lives of the Artists is an attempt to show the "
p17730
g2
tp17731
a(S"superiority of Florentine artistic culture, and Heinrich W lfflin's writings "
p17732
g2
tp17733
a(S'(especially his monograph on Albrecht D rer) attempt to distinguish Italian '
p17734
g2
tp17735
a(S'from German styles of art.'
p17736
