g2
tp17784
a(S'What may once have been viewed simply as a masterpiece is now '
p17785
g2
tp17786
a(S'understood as an economic, social, philosophical, and cultural manifestation '
p17787
g2
tp17788
a(S"of the artist's world  view, philosophy, intentions and background."
