a(S'Steganophony  the concealment of messages in Voice-over-IP conversations, e.g. the employment of delayed or corrupted packets that would normally be ignored by the receiver (this method is called LACK  Lost Audio Packets Steganography), or, alternatively, hiding information in unused header fields.[19]'
p33164
g32336
