tp34238
a(S'This property was used by the move command algorithm which first creates a second filename and then only removes the first filename.'
p34239
g32336
tp34240
a(g34
g32336
tp34241
a(S"Other filesystems, by design, provide only one filename per file, which guarantees that alteration of one filename's file does not alter the other filename's file."
p34242
g32336
tp34243
a(g34
